				<a name="p137141"></a>
				<b class="postauthor">93143</b>
			</td>
			<td width="100%" height="25">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p137141">Re: HDMA Sprite demo not working...</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=137141#p137141"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Dec 01, 2014 12:59 am&nbsp;</div></td>
